post.description:
Stream a response from Claude Sonnet as Server-Sent Events (SSE).

Each chunk: data: {"content": "word "}


Final event: data: {"content": "", "done": true}



The agent loads the last 10 conversation messages and injects relevant
DB context (property / portfolio / market / profile) into the system prompt.
Both the user message and the full assistant reply are saved after streaming.
